Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.23,0:00:05.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.64,0:00:11.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:33.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.13,0:00:42.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.24,0:00:48.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.85,0:00:55.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.16,0:01:03.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.46,0:01:14.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.37,0:01:23.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源波出力上升中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力巨星艦內\N開始出現局部區域重力異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去\N防護罩會完蛋的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續把出力提高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:57.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續把出力提高的話\N重力子能源會有失控危險的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.48,0:01:58.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.92,0:02:01.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擋住敵方能源波才是最優先事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解出力提升!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼斗牙英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.46,0:02:14.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.67,0:02:25.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒這傢伙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:29.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球就不會被\N大量殺戮機繼續襲擊了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就把這當作最後一戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到大結局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...提起幹勁來拼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有來自重力巨星的通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛著神機Σ超重神闖進來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說爸爸他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「魂之凱歌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要平安回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我們還要再一起出去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.72,0:03:16.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...\N你絕對絕對要活著回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警的情形如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全機皆受到重創
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過生命反應都沒有出現異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:36.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛妳已經表現的很好了\N妳已經完成自己的任務了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們請你們救救人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請救救這地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們一定要平安無事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長振作點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.97,0:04:03.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛隊長現在的那張臉\N一點都不像妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是對平常充滿霸氣的隊長\N相當著迷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個! 不准對上司無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對就是這個表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長還是要這樣才對嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙超重神鐵定會得勝的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就相信桑德曼先生\N和他們的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還真是游刃有餘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...請您保祐我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:42.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒耐性再和它耗下去了\N斗牙! 我們快點幹掉它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N要動手了各位!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎霸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉它了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...一點效果都沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼強...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才要開始來真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不快點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼就會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類是種受污染的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.83,0:05:44.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我就要為這些充滿\N慾望與鬥爭的歷史劃上休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.11,0:05:49.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已經被\N大量殺戮機系統污染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.18,0:05:56.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類並不像你想像中的那樣污穢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有露菲拉擬似人格的人造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會把她留在身邊的你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:05.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有失去人類靈魂的證據嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我妹妹的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此愛著我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經如此深愛著露菲拉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就應該...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她病入膏肓之前\N就注意到她已經生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把露菲拉害死的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了喔愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽...超重...旋腕擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.48,0:07:31.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的沒有嗎?\N沒有能一口氣幹掉它的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...讓我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.43,0:07:52.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量殺戮機...只要感測到我\N系統就會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀舅舅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了要保護我\N所以才加入這個指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台大量殺戮機\N就有可能會停止運作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了\N怎麼能讓妳去冒這個險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是程式已經被改寫的話\N那妳該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要舅舅他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還保有一絲關心我的感情的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,程式就應該還是原來那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...想相信我的舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他到底變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信舅舅...\N他的心一定還存在著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不能去啊莉露小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回來莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行無法讓它停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回來啊莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露! 莉露小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險! 快回駕駛艙去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀舅舅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學風暴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在豪魔內部\N確認發生了大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方能源波正開始消退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會因為那個救莉露的程式\N而要了我的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.35,0:10:28.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是保留了人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎麼否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓這個豪魔\N直接去衝撞那顆行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要消滅上面的所有生命\N這樣應該就綽綽有餘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你繼續礙事的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來為我們之間的宿命\N做個了斷的時刻終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就去陪露菲拉吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以死贖罪吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您不要傷害他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拷貝而來的露菲拉記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然擁有了自我意識嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在與你共渡的\N漫長時光中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經寄宿了人類的魂魄而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:52.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連拷貝的妳\N也還是選擇了疾克嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我看看你這小子\N到底還能有什麼本事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是?大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克原來是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大量殺戮機停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也自思考控制中\N解脫了嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.41,0:12:58.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我一直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.71,0:13:07.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在等待著像這樣\N再度取回人心的時刻吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都結束了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經脫離了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快點回話啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...我們得道別了莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我剩下要做的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有為自己的罪付出代價...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.91,0:14:15.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸您已經付出夠多了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拋棄我們城裡的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:22.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是桑德曼先生不在的話\N那我們該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼不論是城裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是飛!\N大家都在等著你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不可能沒有你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:38.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從好幾千年起\N就一直在等待著這一刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待這個變回人類的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待這個被安逸感籠罩的時刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔那多斯(死神)在呼喚我了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就...讓我安眠吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少給我胡鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然想獨自解脫\N簡直要把我給氣炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一大堆帳還沒跟你算呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是被硬逼著\N來當超重神的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是吃了一大堆苦頭的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連綾香的下落都還沒問到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然想自己\N這樣隨隨便便的逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我會讓你這麼做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有好多事情\N想要你告訴我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起回去吧\N桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才能和您相認...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不要和您分開了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:33.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香妳聽到了沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點阻止桑德曼啊綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠阻止他的就只有妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香?她在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...姊姊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文就是綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這到底是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼傻\N妳為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.28,0:16:22.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要死在這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.48,0:16:26.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要這樣子留下來\N不離開你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都還很需要你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.22,0:16:33.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻想視而不見\N就這樣逃避...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.39,0:16:36.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所愛著的\N並不是這樣子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!\N桑德曼先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!\N桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還留下了一些...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非完成不可的事情得去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷...雷文就是綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧?真的嗎?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個假面之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳承了自初代雷文開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.49,0:17:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代代雷文所保留下的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戴著這面具的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就成為雷文的其中之一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這個假面呢...琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.41,0:17:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從妳父親那裡繼承下來的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我爸爸那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此我的爸爸也曾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.22,0:17:37.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來...\N我一直都在綾香的身邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我一直都沒告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.86,0:17:42.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是當我戴著假面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就非得扮演著雷文的角色才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.49,0:17:47.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意原諒姊姊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說我們是姊弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去屬於我們的星球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請注意這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.47,0:18:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪魔開始...\N變成超巨型的大量殺戮機了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還沒有結束啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是系統開始失控暴走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.12,0:18:46.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算用盡所有殘存能源\N朝著重力巨星和地球撞上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.15,0:18:50.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源進入發射狀態\N迴避...來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行最終合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終合神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:06.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重神\N與神機Σ超重神合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的最終進化型態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙啟動工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最凶合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終極超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓中央塔開始運作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把維持防護罩的能源\N全部釋放出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是超重戰艦.重力巨星\N最後的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能源...照射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能源...完全填充!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重炎皇斬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.45,0:20:57.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成...成...成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.33,0:21:10.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊強成這樣\N已經完全無法計算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還真行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:15.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們果然好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙桑德曼叔叔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神棒透了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果到了最後\N還是須要仰賴他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的並不是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是全面性的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們所有人類的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.44,0:21:51.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你...我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.78,0:21:57.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這宇宙中\N不論是什麼樣的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.15,0:22:01.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是什麼人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.32,0:22:04.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都美麗的閃爍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的生命啊茁壯成長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.13,0:22:16.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管在任何地方\N都要如此的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.87,0:22:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.28,0:22:42.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.79,0:22:50.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.30,0:22:58.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.24,0:23:07.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.58,0:23:14.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.99,0:23:16.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.59,0:23:22.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.27,0:23:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.64,0:23:39.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.12,0:23:43.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.49,0:23:52.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.57,0:24:36.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.65,0:24:48.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.32,0:24:52.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比這宇宙中的一切事物\N都還要更美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.09,0:24:54.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.23,0:25:02.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜恭喜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.60,0:25:05.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳了姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.87,0:25:08.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.10,0:25:12.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.61,0:25:16.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你費茲傑羅總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.51,0:25:20.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和綾香姊姊\N看起來都好幸福的樣子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.85,0:25:24.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的夢想\N果然還是穿上新娘禮服啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.65,0:25:28.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那琉菜小姐的對象\N難道是英司少爺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.66,0:25:32.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不要胡扯了!\N為什麼我要和英司那種傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.93,0:25:34.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.40,0:25:36.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那應該是我要說的話吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.43,0:25:39.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的花束喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做新娘捧花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.54,0:25:43.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從新娘子手中接到捧花的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.44,0:25:46.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說將會是下一個結婚的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.44,0:25:49.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.21,0:25:52.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捧花我要囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.01,0:25:54.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們想都別想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.85,0:25:56.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶這個我可不能輸給妳們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.45,0:25:57.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.62,0:26:00.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也希望自己能得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.42,0:26:01.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.32,0:26:03.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.63,0:26:04.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們別想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.46,0:26:05.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.33,0:26:07.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好運~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.30,0:26:08.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳休想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.34,0:26:20.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司要和我結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.34,0:26:22.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你在胡說什麼啊?斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.38,0:26:22.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.98,0:26:26.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚是要一個男人和一個女人\N才能結的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.51,0:26:27.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.58,0:26:31.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊但是也有一些國家\N是可以讓兩個男人結婚的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.99,0:26:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在問題不是那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.29,0:26:39.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行斗牙!\N你千萬別和英司和我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.63,0:26:43.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美...


